Commentary Text: Arshad Khan to Jaiswal, out Caught&Bowled!! That was a highish full toss. The batter wanted to flay it away and got it off the soft top-edge as he couldn't control the big ball. Commentary Text: Boult to Suryakumar Yadav, out Caught by Sandeep Sharma!! What a catch!! Potentially catch of the season here from Sandeep Sharma. This was pace off and length outside off, Suryakumar tried to ramp it over short fine leg. Didn't middle it but felt like he had got enough. The ball hung in the air for a while and Sharma sprinted back from his position inside the circle, then throws in the full stretch dive. Times it perfectly and hangs onto the ball clutched in his left hand and his whole body thuds onto the ground, but the ball remains firmly in his grasp. This catch could decide the game!! Suryakumar Yadav c Sandeep Sharma b Boult 55(29) [4s-8 6s-2]
